{"id": "tesla-2026-04-23-021", "date": "2026-04-23", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 4, "week": 17, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": ["tesla"], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": [], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.5, "reasons": []}, "title": "Tesla says efforts underway to launch FSD in China as soon as possible", "content": "<p><img src=\"https://cnevpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/2026042304154969.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></p>\n<p>Tesla said it is working to launch FSD in the Chinese market as soon as possible, following regulatory approval in the Netherlands.</p>\n<p>For details, please visit <a href=\"https://cnevpost.com\">CnEVPost</a>.</p>\n", "sources": [{"name": "cnevpost", "url": "https://cnevpost.com/2026/04/23/tesla-efforts-underway-launch-fsd-china-as-soon-as-possible/", "type": "rss"}]}
